cold fresh smoothie.

00:16:16.750 --> 00:16:18.460
This is actually a real
example.

00:16:18.460 --> 00:16:20.131
I was frustrated our engineers
were

00:16:20.131 --> 00:16:21.465
working really hard at square.

00:16:21.465 --> 00:16:22.182
And, you know,

00:16:22.182 --> 00:16:24.847
maybe 20% to 30% would stay
very late into evening, and

00:16:24.847 --> 00:16:27.254
I wanted to serve, we were
ready to serve them dinner but

00:16:27.254 --> 00:16:29.509
I wanted to give them
something cool to reward them,

00:16:29.509 --> 00:16:31.200
and you could think about
alcohol, but

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.870
that&#39;s a little complicated.

00:16:32.870 --> 00:16:34.820
So smoothies were probably a
little bit

00:16:34.820 --> 00:16:37.510
better than the pizza, which
