00:36:36.490 --> 00:36:37.450
And he&#39;s like, nope.

00:36:37.450 --> 00:36:38.430
No managers.

00:36:38.430 --> 00:36:39.440
We&#39;re only going to promote
people.

00:36:39.440 --> 00:36:41.010
So the VP of Engineering is

00:36:41.010 --> 00:36:42.150
going to be the single best
engineer.

00:36:42.150 --> 00:36:44.180
The VP of Design&#39;s going to be
the single best designer.

00:36:44.180 --> 00:36:45.840
The VP of Product&#39;s going to
be the single best product

00:36:45.840 --> 00:36:47.970
person and they&#39;re going to
learn to manage later.

00:36:47.970 --> 00:36:51.923
And the advantage of that is
you don&#39;t demoralize people,

00:36:51.923 --> 00:36:54.120
because everybody knows that
